PLACED ON THE HURTWOOD TO MARK
THE 50th ANNIVERSARY OF THE OPENING
OF THE HOLMBURY ST MARY YOUTH HOSTEL
Like others throughout the world, it exists
to encourage a wider knowledge, Iove and care
of the countryside amongst young people
of all ages.
YOUTH HOSTELS ASSOCIATION 1985"▒
